es, once the game starts getting interesting its over after few missions).* AI is beyond handicapped. (dudes run around randomly, you have to set your dudes to fire at them every time you lose sight with any dude that is aiming which is tedious af, AI noclips through stuff).* Tedious (gameplay and the high frequency of save-load required when the protagonist randomly gets 360noscopedwithapistolfromthehipat50meterseventhougheverybodylookedatthatdirectionandsawnoenemies).I got the game from a bundle, but had played it before and knew what it was about.Spoiler:https://www.gamefaqs.com/pc/781524-man-of-prey/faqs/72394Lets Play, So You Wouldnt Have To:https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLpobIqXwKarHv_AZ7J7dInyl9r9BA1Cnx"
